Amazon A2I = A service that brings human review into AI/ML workflows.

Sometimes ML predictions are not 100% confident â†’ A2I lets humans validate those predictions.

Example: An ML model says "90% sure this is a cat" â†’ A2I can route such low-confidence cases to a human reviewer.

